.TH REVIEW_SOURCE_CLAIMS_TUI 1 "2026-03-29" "stophammer" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
review_source_claims_tui \- interactive source-claim and resolved-promotion inspection console
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B review_source_claims_tui
[
.BI --db " PATH"
] [
.BI --limit " N"
]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B review_source_claims_tui
opens a terminal UI for feeds that carry staged source claims or resolved
promotion rows. It is intended for operators inspecting provenance and
promotion state without issuing ad hoc SQL queries.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI --db " PATH"
Path to the SQLite database. Defaults to
.BR ./stophammer.db .
.TP
.BI --limit " N"
Maximum number of feeds to load into the review queue. Defaults to 200.
.SH CONTROLS
The interface shows the feed queue, the feed's tracks, and the evidence panel.
Use the on-screen key hints to switch focus, move through feeds and tracks, and
scroll long evidence blocks.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Open the TUI against the default database:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_source_claims_tui -- --db ./stophammer.db
.fi
.TP
Limit the initial queue size:
.nf
cargo run --bin review_source_claims_tui -- --db ./stophammer.db --limit 100
.fi
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR backfill_canonical (1),
.BR review_artist_identity_tui (1),
.BR review_wallet_identity_tui (1)
